n=int(input("Enter a number:"))
tot=0
while(n>0):
    dig=n%10
    tot=tot+dig
    n=n//10
print("The total sum of digits is:",tot)
Output :
Enter a number:5634
The total sum of digits is: 18

[Program finished]
